description: Smartwool's new Men's Intraknit™ Hybrid Fiber Full Zip Hoodie is bringing all of the state-of-the-art construction and benefits of Smartwool's Intraknit™ technology to your jacket collection. Expanding Smartwool's 3D-knitting platform, Smartwool's Hybrid Fiber combines a durable synthetic outer with a soft Merino wool interior. This versatile garment is capable, comfortable, and ready to help elevate your Intraknit™ collection, as well as your performance.
name: Smartwool Intraknit HyFi Full Zip Hoodie - Mens
